<item>
            <title>[PIG-816] PigStorage() does not accept Unicode characters in its contructor </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-816</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Simple Pig script which uses Unicode characters in the PigStorage() constructor fails with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
studenttab = LOAD &apos;/user/viraj/studenttab10k&apos; AS (name:chararray, age:&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;,gpa:&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;float&lt;/span&gt;);
X2 = GROUP studenttab by age;
Y2 = FOREACH X2 GENERATE group, COUNT(studenttab);
store Y2 into &apos;/user/viraj/y2&apos; using PigStorage(&apos;\u0001&apos;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;========================================================================================&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR org.apache.pig.tools.grunt.GruntParser - ERROR 2997: Unable to recreate exception from backend error: org.apache.hadoop.ipc.RemoteException: java.io.IOException: java.lang.RuntimeException: org.xml.sax.SAXParseException: Character reference &quot;&amp;amp;#1&quot; is an invalid XML character.&lt;br/&gt;
========================================================================================&lt;br/&gt;
Attaching log file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
